      "voiceName": "Philip DeFranco",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Saw Project Hail Mary in IMAX 70mm last night and its fucking fantastic!\n\nIt does the book justice and it should be watched on the biggest screen you can get yourself in front of asap. Amaze! Amaze! Amaze!",
