    {
      "voiceId": "philip-defranco",
      "voiceName": "Philip DeFranco",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Woke up in the middle of the night to Trump openly going full Farquaad.\n\n  \n\n\n\nAcyn (@Acyn)\n\nTrump: The lives of American heroes may be lost, and we may have casualties \u2014 that often happens in war.\n\nVideo\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\u2014 https://nitter.net/Acyn/status/2027652088046796867#m",
