      "timestamp": "2026-02-28T11:42:04+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "philip-defranco",
      "voiceName": "Philip DeFranco",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "This art from The New Yorker really sparked a lot of debate and I wanted to know what you think about.\n\nIs it right? Is it wrong? Is the current state of things more nuanced or complicated?",
